<h2>Company Overview</h2>
<p>
[Edit this section.] Adab Real Estate Agency is a Nigerian property consultancy helping clients buy, sell, rent, and manage residential and commercial real estate. We serve homeowners, tenants, landlords, and diaspora Nigerians investing from abroad — with transparent pricing in NGN and clear communication via phone, email, and WhatsApp.
</p>

<h2>Our Services</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Property Sales</strong> — Listings, valuations, and buyer representation across Lagos, Abuja, and other Nigerian markets.</li>
<li><strong>Rentals &amp; Lettings</strong> — Tenant sourcing, lease agreements, and move-in coordination.</li>
<li><strong>Property Management</strong> — Rent collection, maintenance oversight, and landlord reporting.</li>
<li><strong>Investment Advisory</strong> — Guidance for diaspora and local investors on Nigerian real estate opportunities.</li>
<li><strong>Documentation Support</strong> — Assistance with title verification, surveys, and handover processes.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Why Adab</h2>
<ul>
<li>Registered with the Corporate Affairs Commission (RC 9590252)</li>
<li>Local market knowledge with diaspora-friendly communication</li>
<li>Transparent fees quoted in Nigerian Naira (NGN)</li>
<li>Responsive support on WhatsApp: +234 812 827 2287</li>
</ul>

